 computing. We also point out that the dipolar\ninteractions between nitrogen-vacancy centers forming a rectangular lattice in\na diamond matrix may permit a solid-state realization of the anisotropic\ncompass-Heisenberg model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Jun 2012 14:53:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2012 09:02:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
